;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;A fair exchange is never a robbe=\r\nry, as Vimalananda says. Theoretically, when the *right person* performs ma=\r\nny of the things mentioned in that blog, (and some of the stuff there is no=\r\nt exactly accurately portrayed), he/she will know how to balance the karmic=\r\n impact well. In the hands of an immature individual, it can lead to disast=\r\ner. Further, the so called division between &#39;classical Tantra&#39; and =\r\n&#39;folk Tantra&#39; is not as sharp and clear as it is made out there. Ea=\r\nch influences the other and is very much intermingled.=A0 Every sadhana in =\r\nVama Margi Tantra has a firm spiritual basis. Performed correctly, with the=\r\n right attitude, and by the right individual, it leads to very high spiritu=\r\nal states.&lt;/div&gt;\n\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;-Regards&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;=A0Rajarshi&lt;br&gt;&lt;=\r\n/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;span&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;=A0&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;i&gt;&lt;=\r\nstrong&gt;\n&lt;div class=3D&quot;MsoNormal&quot;&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=3D&quot;FONT-FAMILY:Verdana=\r\n;COLOR:navy;FONT-SIZE:10pt&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=3D&quot;#000000&quot; face=3D&quot;Times New Roman=\r\n&quot;&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=3D&quot;COLOR:#000066&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=3D&quot;FONT-SIZE:medium&quot;&gt;&lt;=\r\nfont color=3D&quot;#a2a2a2&quot; size=3D&quot;3&quot;&gt;Bazeecha-e-atfal hain duniya mere aage.&lt;/=\r\nfont&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;b&gt;&lt;span style=3D&quot;COLOR:#000066&quot;&gt;&lt;span s=\r\ntyle=3D&quot;FONT-SIZE:medium&quot;&gt;&lt;font size=3D&quot;3&quot;&gt;&lt;font color=3D&quot;#a2a2a2&quot;&gt;Hota hai=\r\nn shab-o-roz tamasha mere aage&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/font&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/b&gt;&lt;/div&gt;\n&lt;div&gt;&lt;=\r\nb&gt;&lt;span style=3D&quot;COLOR:#000066&quot;&gt;&lt;span style=3D&quot;F